4.76/5  rDev +7.7%look: 5 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.75 | feel: 4.75 |  overall: 5His does look terrific. Glass pour, hazy yellowish/ cidery appearance, nice white head and what turns out to be lacing aplenty. 
